109
00:06:11.521 --> 00:06:13.430
<font color="#00ffff">Die beiden obersten</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Krisenkommunikatoren</font>

110
00:06:14.071 --> 00:06:16.160
<font color="#00ffff">sind aber diese beiden Herren:</font>

111
00:06:16.802 --> 00:06:18.660
<font color="#00ffff">Mister Corona, Daniel Koch,</font>

112
00:06:19.302 --> 00:06:22.281
<font color="#00ffff">und Alain Berset,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">der Gesundheitsminister.</font>

113
00:06:22.923 --> 00:06:25.751
<font color="#00ffff">Edith Graf-Litscher, wie haben</font>
<font color="#00ffff">die beiden ihre Arbeit gemacht?</font>

114
00:06:26.393 --> 00:06:29.766
<font color="#ffffff">Die beiden</font>
